== UGHE ==
[[Kaminuza y'u Rwanda|kaminuza Global Heath Eqwity]] izwi nka UGHE ni kaminuza yatangiye gukorera mu Rwanda muri 2015 ni 

ubwoko bushya bwa [[Kaminuza y'u Rwanda|Kaminuza]] Bwibanda cyane mu gutanga ubuvuzi buhanitse murwego rwogukemura 

ibibazo by'imibereho  nibiteza ubusumbane n'imikorere idahwitse muBUVUZI MU [[Rwanda]]<ref>https://www.who.int/health-topics/health-equity#tab=tab_1</ref>

== Imiyoborere ==
ku itariki ya 3 Mata UGHE yashyizeho Uwahoze ari [[Ministry of Education (Rwanda)|Minisitiri w'ubuzima]] Agnes Binagwaho nk'umuyobozi<ref>https://www.thelancet.com/pdfs/journals/lancet/PIIS0140-6736(04)16325-3.pdf</ref>

wungirije wa [[Kaminuza y'u Rwanda|Kaminuza ya Global Health Eqwity]] murwego rwo kugenzura iyaguka rya gahunda zuburezi

nubushakashati bya [[Kaminuza y'u Rwanda|Kaminu]]<nowiki/>za ya UGHE ndetse no guteza imbere ubufatanye bw'isi  ndetse n'ikigo cyayo

cya butaro giherereye mu Rwanda [[Intara y’Amajyaruguru y’u Rwanda|muntara ya'amajyaruguru]]<ref>https://ughe.org/</ref>

